Goal:
Automatically create the correct payment method object (UPI, Card, Wallet) without writing new code in OrderService every time.

Think of Zomato Payment Factory like a kitchen that prepares whatever dish you order.
You just tell the kitchen â†’ â€œI want Pizzaâ€
Kitchen â†’ gives Pizza object.

Same:
User chooses â†’ â€œUPIâ€
Factory â†’ returns UPI Payment Gateway object

ğŸ”¥ Factory Flow in Zomato App
1ï¸ User chooses Payment Method in Console

Example:

Enter Payment Method (UPI/CARD/WALLET):

2ï¸ OrderService sends request to PaymentFactory
