3ï¸âƒ£ Factory checks the method
if (method == "UPI") â†’ return new UpiPayment()
if (method == "CARD") â†’ return new CardPayment()
if (method == "WALLET") â†’ return new WalletPayment()

4ï¸ Correct Payment Object is returned

OrderService now receives the correct implementation.

Example:

UPI payment selected

5ï¸ OrderService uses that object
