6ï¸ Order continues

Payment successful

Delivery assigned

Discount applied

ğŸ§  WHY FACTORY PATTERN IS USED?
Problem	Factory Solution
If new payment method comes (e.g., Crypto), you must modify many files.	Add one new class only and update the factory class.
Tight coupling	Loose coupling
Code becomes messy	Clean, maintainable
